videos.headline: Lawrence keeps it for 7-yard TD
videos.description: Trevor Lawrence fakes the handoff and powers into the end zone for a Clemson touchdown.

tracking.trackingName: NCF One-Play (Lawrence keeps it for 7-yard TD) 2019/11/09 ESHEET

videos.headline: Higgins burns NC State defense for 33-yard TD
videos.description: Trevor Lawrence finds Tee Higgins open down the sideline for a 33-yard touchdown.

tracking.trackingName: NCF One-Play (Higgins burns NC State defense for 33-yard TD) 2019/11/09 ESHEET

videos.headline: Clemson  makes NC State pay for fumble in red zone
videos.description: Clemson recovers an NC State fumbled handoff and two plays later Trevor Lawrence shovel passes to Travis Etienne for a 4-yard touchdown.

tracking.trackingName: NCF One-Play (Clemson makes NC State pay for fumble in red zone) 2019/11/09 ESHEET

videos.headline: Etienne goes up the middle for 19-yard TD run
videos.description: Travis Etienne takes the handoff up the middle for a 19-yard Clemson touchdown.

tracking.trackingName: NCF One-Play (Etienne goes up the middle for 19-yard TD run) 2019/11/09 ESHEET

videos.headline: Clemson O-lineman Simpson barrels in for TD
videos.description: Clemson offensive lineman John Simpson takes the handoff up the middle for a one-yard touchdown.

videos.headline: Knight gets NC State on the board with 53-yard TD run
videos.description: Zonovan Knight follows blockers up the left side for a 53-yard NC State touchdown.

tracking.trackingName: NCF One-Play (Knight gets NC State on the board with 53-yard TD run) 2019/11/09 ESHEET

videos.headline: Etienne goes off for 3 TDs and 143 yards vs. NC State
videos.description: Travis Etienne runs for two touchdowns and catches a third as Clemson remains unbeaten.

tracking.trackingName: COM_NCF Highlight (Etienne goes off for 3 TDs and 143 yards vs. NC State) 2019/11/09 ESHEET SOTFULL

videos.headline: Dabo proud of Clemson for clinching 5th straight ACC title appearance
videos.description: Dabo Swinney says the win vs. NC State is extra special as Clemson clinches the ACC Atlantic division crown.
